{"tid":2302602,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"粉絲向伯賢推薦自己兼職的漢堡店！伯賢回覆後...還把地點、時間和粉絲名字打到備忘錄！","createTime":"2020-11-27T08:54:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-27T12:05:21.000Z","uid":16659,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"aba33db036dd2a8906a43d05fdfb2215952b64d3","tid":2302602,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T08:54:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/800_86400_75f25c32e665b52befbe8d93e7cde0fd/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-11-27/131944-886637.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F800_86400_75f25c32e665b52befbe8d93e7cde0fd%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-11-27%2F131944-886637.jpg&h=863c7bd2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nEXO伯賢常和粉絲們互動，今日（27日）他也在推特回答粉絲們的問題，還有人因此追星成功呢 XD<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有粉絲留言：「伯賢呀！富川有一個叫제이룸漢堡店，在富川市廳站，我在那邊做兼職呢...真的真的很好吃，來富川的話一定要來玩ㅠㅠㅠ會給你做超好吃的ㅠㅠㅠㅠㅠ」伯賢也回應：「제이룸漢堡？什麼時候兼職呀？」<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_d3f207315d5fbe0e83bf330afd9b55bf/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-11-27/131944-886634.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_d3f207315d5fbe0e83bf330afd9b55bf%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-11-27%2F131944-886634.png&h=e8d1a068&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n粉絲：「從週一到週六...每天都兼職伯賢啊...從4點開始到9點關門為止ㅠㅠㅠ」結果伯賢又回復：「什麼時候一定會去一次，等著哦！」還附上了自己的備忘錄，當中打著「富川제이룸漢堡 4～9點 콩떡（粉絲推特暱稱）」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_52dbde8ac80eb557d7861addb1c48bb7/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-11-27/131944-886636.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_52dbde8ac80eb557d7861addb1c48bb7%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-11-27%2F131944-886636.png&h=8fdb6e06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這讓不少網友表示：「伯賢來之前好像都無法放棄兼職了」、「真羨慕你！成粉啊」、「我現在搬到富川去兼職」、「離我家很近的地方，我也每天都要去嗎」、「就算討厭老闆，也要為了伯賢撐下去」、「我不是粉絲都心動了」、「知道他為什麼這麼有人氣了，大發」、「還寫了備忘錄，太可愛了」等等。"},{"pid":"2499f73811d92331f55ddb05997e335546459276","tid":2302602,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T08:55:06.000Z","msg":"邊伯"},{"pid":"43345b4e29038d2c8e9bd1286db7fb73b59e1bf3","tid":2302602,"uid":229026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T08:57:16.000Z","msg":"@牙邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92ce7f1fad29feee6bfc7b1a7495a63dd8013965","tid":2302602,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"43345b4e29038d2c8e9bd1286db7fb73b59e1bf3","tid":2302602,"uid":229026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T08:57:16.000Z","msg":"@牙邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T08:58:29.000Z","msg":"客套說話<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0fb59ba1f67a7724408c968495599bd2af8594c","tid":2302602,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T09:02:40.000Z","msg":"係咪奶支那閪個隊EXO？"},{"pid":"8f67be3f2eb7344f5de29f6467b98b04991beced","tid":2302602,"uid":123774,"like":7,"dislike":6,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T09:04:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N0sC2aM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN0sC2aM.png&h=2c80cfac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n聽BTS好過呢隊過氣野啦"},{"pid":"6f7884fdd87b91dccd2eddb88b7ec460daecebd6","tid":2302602,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"8f67be3f2eb7344f5de29f6467b98b04991beced","tid":2302602,"uid":123774,"like":7,"dislike":6,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T09:04:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N0sC2aM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN0sC2aM.png&h=2c80cfac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\